  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Symptomatic ≥ 70% stenosis of the SFA (Rutherford stage 2-6)

          -  Written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute ischemia and/or acute thrombosis of the SFA

          -  Untreated ipsilateral iliac artery stenosis &gt;70%

          -  Previous stenting of the SFA

          -  Popliteal stenosis &gt;70%

          -  Severe renal insufficiency
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
